---
## Sample per-robot override for the optional github-review-digest job.
## Copy this file to custom/conf/jobs/github-review-digest.yaml after
## configuring GitHub identity support for the robot.

Config:
  Provider: github
  User: alice
  APIBaseURL: https://api.github.com
  ReviewQuery: "is:open is:pr review-requested:@me archived:false"
  MaxItems: 5
